{"tid":1675913,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"認真去 FC 某不知名記者既記者證，結果","createTime":"2019-10-26T07:02:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-26T13:04:56.000Z","uid":325913,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"3e317c7a37c72784cee5dff87ba612be9a73b35d","tid":1675913,"uid":325913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T07:02:38.000Z","msg":"間公司根本唔存在，虛假名稱，錯地址。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YMVjMiM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYMVjMiM.png&h=13fe244d&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n張證上面間公司 (ZEN-press 善フレス) 係搵唔到，上埋 google jp 摷係摷唔到<br />\n個電話都係假，空號<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ottQSYM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FottQSYM.png&h=2811343e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nShibuya 嘅 motoyoyogi-machi 打錯做 motoyoyoghi-machi。日本傳媒公司有咁唔小心？<br />\n <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cwAf35s.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcwAf35s.png&h=c902e1d9&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n然後幫佢執錯字，順住證上寫 24-1-802  motoyoyogi-machi shibuya-ku tokyo去摷，係摷唔到相關資料。<br />\n<br />\n果個&quot;記者&quot;係6/7元朗出現過。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2RoxmWO.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2RoxmWO.png&h=d7fd8d14&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"dec67ed57e6e250bcdd41affaf3d5e9ee786ae14","tid":1675913,"uid":14103,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T07:03:37.000Z","msg":"結論 係支那人？"},{"pid":"cd0d32d909be35aab7dd93408fd78dcb3ea9e4a3","tid":1675913,"uid":23684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T07:04:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />日本人？"},{"pid":"7751144070abe07dae02480337dde0acef8056ae","tid":1675913,"uid":42740,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T07:05:28.000Z","msg":"之前都有支那狗扮日本人影大頭"},{"pid":"c1009df11bd108028c969b1dfa1c5bec4834cbfc","tid":1675913,"uid":149607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T07:05:44.000Z","msg":"N3撚表示一樣感到疑惑"},{"pid":"c4f777d0e0528956add5a7ba00c322107f0f1c38","tid":1675913,"uid":325913,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T07:06:16.000Z","msg":"條友係好可疑。無理由一間日本傳媒公司整張記者證都可以錯漏百出到如此。<br />\n如果佢係公民記者，咁佢唔應該無端端作張證出黎。<br />\n咁樣盜用人地外媒個朵，只會陷外國傳媒於危險中。<br />\n如果佢係 popo <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"127f17171ddea7926d2d405968bf28e72cd7a2fd","tid":1675913,"uid":74155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T07:06:50.000Z","msg":"邊度有男人嘅名用平假名㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n女人先會用平假名做名<br />\n好撚假<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"943b5fab81e01b0f0ae30aa05ad2463c7269872e","tid":1675913,"uid":55130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T07:06:53.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"ccd6097fdb4073fa3d5f44346715cba0df99ab55","tid":1675913,"uid":325913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T07:10:55.000Z","msg":"我唔係鼓勵大家捉鬼。前線點可能無鬼。無得避。唔好捉。<br />\n但我想提出兩樣野：<br />\n１：唔好玩外媒個朵。玩衰咗令到大家對外媒信任低咗，會好大鑊。<br />\n２：真係鬼，或者吊詭既事，係防唔晒。凡事遮實晒就最穩陣。<br />\n３：受傳媒訪前簡單地問定身份背景，我肯定外媒唔會介意。"},{"pid":"a1a1b3f4ec9e6170f129ebd840a023e1204d8a40","tid":1675913,"uid":325913,"like":0,"disli